Active Directory Automation & Management Toolkit

A lightweight, script-driven repository designed to streamline routine Active Directory operations. 
This project focuses on user lifecycle management, group policy validation, OU structure maintenance, 
and security auditing through modular PowerShell automation.

Core Features
- Automated user provisioning, attribute updates, and safe deprovisioning workflows
- OU hierarchy validation and stale object cleanup utilities
- Group membership auditing with export-ready reporting
- Password policy and account lockout threshold compliance checks
- Secure credential handling with built-in execution logging

Usage Guidelines
Clone the repository, review environment prerequisites, and execute all scripts in an isolated test environment 
first. Each module includes parameter validation, dry-run capabilities, and inline documentation to prevent
unintended changes. Always run with least-privilege accounts and verify output before applying modifications to 
production domains.

